    "en": {
      "title": "B/ Hindu College student stands second in Sri Lanka",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Jayachandran Dwarakes, who studied Mathematics at Bampalapitiya Hindu College, secured 3 A's and stood second at the district level and nationally in Sri Lanka, according to the results of the high-level examination held last year.",
        "It is noteworthy that Dwarakes, who is the best debater and the best student leader, scored 191 marks in the scholarship examination in 2012 and got the first position at the district level and also got 9 A marks in the ordinary examination."
